Angelica!
We saw your letter! What's wrong!?

Ah, guys...
Actually... I made a decision...

So I have to get some material.
Could you... please help me?

Ah, yeah, sure...
But is that material so rare that you need our help?

No, not that rare.
But... it's said it's deep in the "Seal of Brambles".

I acted on impulse and I'm sorry to worry you.
So I want to use your help this time...

Haha, I see.
I'm glad you turn to us.

Yeah. Let's go!
Our destination is deep in the "Seal of Brambles"!
